      <title>局外人艺术博览会：这里有 8 个值得一看的景点</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2024/02/29/arts/design/outsider-art-fair-what-to-see.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[垮掉派诗人的自画像、1930 年代马戏团的海报、乔治亚·拉塞尔 (Georgia Russell) 的三英尺娃娃——这些都是这个繁忙的曼哈顿博览会上的一些奇特发现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2024/02/29/arts/design/outsider-art-fair-what-to-see.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 17:42:08 GMT</pubDate>
